<tt>Sat Jun 14 12:26:51 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I am nearing completion of my master thesis, which is a manuscript of poems written about the Vietnam War.  I would like to have them published some day, if only to let my children know their father, and why he acts the way he does.  If anyone knows of a publisher that is interested in such material, please do not hesitate to let me know.  I was a corpsman with the 1st Btn, 3rd Marines (1967-68), and have had a wealth of knowledge to draw upon.  My poems are created to enlighten, shock and tell it the way it was and is, entertaining for those who were there, and those who were not.  Thanks.  Doc Dirr<br>

